title: Volcanic ash cloud: Jetstar cancels flights in and out of Bali
text:
Volcanic ash cloud: Jetstar cancels f... Volcanic ash cloud: Jetstar cancels flights in and out of Bali 28 min ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
Ash emitted from Mount Raung, in east Java, has disrupted air travel in and out of the holiday island of Bali, Indonesia. JQ106/105 - Perth-Denpasar-Perth JQ127/128 - Adelaide-Denpasar-Adelaide JQ116 - Perth-Denpasar / Denpasar-Singapore JQ117 - Singapore-Denpasar / Denpasar-Perth JQ35 - Melbourne-Denpasar JQ58 - Denpasar-Brisbane JQ37/38 - Sydney-Denpasar / Denpasar-Sydney JQ63/64 - Sydney-Denpasar / Denpasar-Sydney "Jetstar will make an assessment of the flying conditions [on Thursday] morning and update customers should further cancellations be necessary," the airline said on its website.   Sydney Morning Herald.
